des:
Almost 300 behavioral question randomly chosen to give you some practice before your interview!

Do you have more question? Please visit us and leave the question or just share it in the comments.

Propose your questions: https://goo.gl/forms/yQ7hdLZELgMeimmk1
Check out the current questions: https://goo.gl/LsKA4r

I've developed this skill to prepare myself for my next interview and I thought it would be helpful for other people to. 

To start, just say "Alexa, open Interview Training"

Please let me a comment if you think I can improve the skill.

Thanks for the support!
